      • availableJoinTypes

        public static final Set<String> availableJoinTypes
        uniform: uniform random sample arbitrary: sampling probabilities for tuples may be all different. (there's no guarantee on uniformness). nosample: the original table itself. stratified: stratified on a certain column. It is guaranteed that we do not miss any group. universe: hashed on a certain column. It is guaranteed that the tuples with the same attribute values in the column are sampled together.
